				<h1 style="font-size:30px; line-height:40px; text-shadow:0px 0px 5px #000">Classroom Activities</h1>
				<div class="horizontaldots"></div>
				<p>Put learning into action by creating visual displays, mentoring younger students and presenting in class.<br />
					<br />
					All activities are designed to be presented in the classroom by students; ideas include:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>high school students presenting to  peers or middle school students</li>
					<li>middle and high school students presenting to elementary school students</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
